---------------------------I. Create New DataBase on MySQL------------------------
Create database name : pitza
   
 ----------------------------II. Run  SpringBoot Server-----------------------------

// Table was created by SpringBoot(After Start SpringBoot Server) 

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

@PostMapping - addUser

In POSTMAN -

Set to POST - http://localhost:9090/usercontroller/addUser

{
    "name":"Kunal",
    "email":"kunalshetty1070@gmail.com",
    "address":"Home",
    "phone":"1234567890",
    "password":"hello"
}

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

@GetMapping - getUser/checkUser/{email}/{password}

In POSTMAN -

Set to GET - http://localhost:9090/usercontroller/getUser/checkuser/kunalshetty1070@gmail.com/hello

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

@GetMapping - checkEmail/{email}

In POSTMAN = 

Set to Get - http://localhost:9090/usercontroller/checkEmail/kunalshetty1070@gmail.com

If Email Not Exist then ERROR

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

@GetMapping - signOut

In POSTMAN -

Set to Get - http://localhost:9090/usercontroller/signOut